sources.fonts\\fonts.sass:
@font-face
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  src: url(../fonts/Montserrat-Regular.ttf)
  font-weight: normal


@font-face
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  src: url(../fonts/Montserrat-Bold.ttf)
  font-weight: bold
sources.blocks\\page\\_page.sass:
.page
  font-family: 'Montserrat'
  margin: 0 auto
  padding: 0
  max-width: 1440px
  min-width: 320px
sources.blocks\\logo\\_logo.sass:
.logo
  display: block
  width: 105.6px
  height: 40px
  background: url(../images/logo.svg)
sources.blocks\\menu\\__list\\_menu__list.sass:
.menu__list
  display: flex
  justify-content: space-between
  margin: 0
  padding: 0
  list-style: none
sources.blocks\\dropdown\\__content\\_dropdown__:
.dropdown__content

.dropdown:hover .dropdown__content
  display: flex
sources.blocks\\button\\_button.sass:
.button
  outline: 0

.button:hover

sources.sass\\_variables.sass:
$primary-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
$primary-color: #BC9CFF
$secondary-gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #6FCF97 0%, #66D2EA 100%)

// Colors
$dark-100: rgba(31, 32, 65, 1)
$dark-75: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
$dark-50:rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)
$dark-25: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
$dark-5: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.05)
$purple: #BC9CFF
$green: #6FCF97
sources.blocks\\login-button\\_login-button.sass:
.login-button
  display: flex
  align-items: center
  height: 34px
  margin-right: 20px
  background: #fff
  color: $primary-color
  position: relative
  box-sizing: border-box
  border: 2px solid transparent
  background-clip: padding-box

.login-button::before
  content: ""
  position: absolute
  margin: -2px
  top: 0px
  bottom: 0px
  left: 0px
  right: 0px
  background: $primary-gradient
  border-radius: inherit
  z-index: -1
sources.blocks\\section\\__title\\_section__titl:
.section__title
  margin: 0
  font-style: normal
  font-weight: bold
  font-size: 24px
  line-height: 29px
  color: $dark-100
sources.blocks\\landing\\_landing.sass:
.landing
  min-height: 830px
  position: relative
  overflow: hidden
  z-index: 1
sources.blocks\\landing\\__background\\_landing_:
.landing__background
  object-fit: cover
  object-position: center
  position: absolute
  z-index: -1
sources.blocks\\landing\\__search\\_landing__sea:
.landing__search
  width: 380px
  padding: 40px 30px 30px
  background: #FFFFFF
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)
  box-sizing: border-box
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)
  border-radius: 4px
  margin-top: 70px
sources.blocks\\form\\__input\\_form__input.sass:
.form__input
  width: 100%
  margin: 0
  padding: 0
  border: 0
  box-sizing: border-box
  border: 1px solid $dark-25
  border-radius: 4px
sources.blocks\\form\\__group\\_form__group.sass:
.form__group
  width: 150px
  height: 65px
  display: flex
  flex-direction: column
  justify-content: space-between

.form__group:last-of-type
  width: 320px
.column__title
  font-weight: bold
  margin: 0 0 21px
  font-size: 12px
  line-height: 15px
  text-transform: uppercase
sources.blocks\\nav\\__link\\_nav__link.sass:
.nav__link
  font-weight: normal
  font-size: 14px
  line-height: 17px
  text-decoration: none
  color: $dark-50
.footer__input
  width: calc(100% - 44px)
  padding: 8px 15px 8px
  outline: 0
  border: 0
  margin: 0
  box-sizing: border-box
  height: 42px
sources.blocks\\footer\\__button\\_footer__butto:
.footer__button
  width: 44px
  height: 42px
  font-size: 24px
  line-height: 24px
  display: flex
  align-items: center
  justify-content: center
